Greedy Questions

1.  N light bulbs are connected by a wire. Given an initial state of all bulbs, find the minimum number of switches you have to press to turn on all the bulbs - Github
2. There are n children standing in a line with each child assigned a rating value. What is the minimum candies you must give? - Github
3. Gasup problem - EPI and Github
4. Return highest product of three numbers from the array - Github
5. Find the majority element in the array - EPI and Github
6. Mice/rat holes - Github